府突然宣布停工會帶來甚麼法律後果</span></span><br />\n<br />\n對面澳門政府一巴一巴咁車埋黎啦<br />\n人地停工左成日  暴緊亂添呀屌你老母<br />\n法律後果？ 我屌你老母屌撚埋你全家就唔洗負法律後果啦而家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T07:16:03.000Z","msg":"之咪係，dq議員同割地兩檢夠無機制評估會有咩法律後果，佢又敢做<br />\n<br />\n對住商界牛屎佬就縮，對市民先「好打得」，屌林病老母！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e49a26090f5b456d509fb5f784207323154d2ecd","tid":827416,"uid":86614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T07:18:31.000Z","msg":"仲講咩非緊急公務員帶頭停工<br />\n其他公司就會跟"},{"pid":"47cece74160683d9e2220a5696ab3bdf893025b9","tid":827416,"uid":74272,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T07:18:42.000Z","msg":"大家請開名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d694998e5b2867e271b910c9f7230f8a2c07d8c4","tid":827416,"uid":10454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c8b41ad3e31c1a901b889b774e7a2776b09d60d","tid":827416,"uid":78257,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T07:15:57.000Z","msg":"有同事住元朗屋企水浸，星期一冇返都照被扣年假<br />\n<br />\n利申公務員"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T07:19:01.000Z","msg":"Csb出左email話唔洗扣喎"},{"pid":"30b511f2423d365246f713f63bb53040150fabff","tid":827416,"uid":16676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T07:19:03.000Z","msg":"藍領放勞假既就自己死掂佢要返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n放紅假果d 係扮工<br />\n放勞假果d 係返工<br />\n正苦帶頭攪掂呢樣先啦<br />\n<br />\n上次增加勞假到18日都唔比, 唔好話睇齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6386a9335e9b058f2a6213b82fdf21b7b9853018","tid":827416,"uid":40968,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T07:21:41.000Z","msg":"根本應該立例規定十號風球後全港一定要放一日假(政府緊急救援人員除外)<br />\n違例僱主須即時監禁"},{"pid":"c0413d074513cbbdeb45cb01f769af7edbc585ff","tid":827416,"uid":57460,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6386a9335e9b058f2a6213b82fdf21b7b9853018","tid":827416,"uid":40968,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1